snippet.title: Filthy Animals | Heist Simulator - Official Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10006314

Filthy Animals is a single player + co-op multiplayer mutant animal comedy heist simulator. Team up with your friends to break in, solve puzzles, grab loot, fight guards, and get out in one piece. Plunge into chaos through huge levels filled with loads of explosions, devious dangers, and malicious traps to become the mutant animal master criminal you always dreamed you could be.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4games #ps4
